{"tid":1614853,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"TG最好熄左通知個preview","createTime":"2019-10-03T02:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T08:55:46.000Z","uid":139882,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ed7adf113ca692ce2c230ae804947d611e868aa4","tid":1614853,"uid":139882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gEwLy1L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgEwLy1L.jpg&h=dda8fdbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大戰過後 我係橋上面搜證 睇下射左咩彈同有冇咩特別特別發現 結果比我發現左部Iphone 我唔知係速龍定係手足跌左 <br />\n根據個位置係橋既中間位 應該係班狗亂射野既位附近 <br />\n而我影低相既時候係彈哂TG既通知出黎 而且係睇到內容<br />\n<br />\n如果咁唔好彩係手足既 咁就麻煩喇 祈求班狗解唔到鎖<br />\n如果係速龍既 咁就可以肯定班狗已經入侵左各大TG既Group<br />\n<br />\n當時橋上好多狗 我比狗𥄫到實 想執都執唔到 最後部Iphone比速龍執左 <br />\n<br />\n提提手足們真係最好唔好因為貪方便而開Preview 好易比人睇哂內容 跌左電話就會好似咁樣咩都比人睇哂<br />\n<br />\n10.1 沙燕橋之役其中一個攝記"},{"pid":"487df8e7f4062a06ce0bd3b26bfeb2360923cf11","tid":1614853,"uid":108571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:18:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a924c441082f36503111538518a650f04467e451","tid":1614853,"uid":17796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:20:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"439502a0e065f2e5a80f4b1617bf004486e9a657","tid":1614853,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04b7f94f07da8e08b27b9f319ad5fc0178d0cb0","tid":1614853,"uid":3700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:21:19.000Z","msg":"TG記得set密碼"},{"pid":"cea276b9ca1edd1fc5e1da1791228e6cc21fa953","tid":1614853,"uid":139882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit